node.text: @yumi.lovesfood glad you like it. Thank you 😊

"I like the mountains, because they make me feel small; they help me sort out what's important in life". 🏔️⁠
.⁠
Supposed to go on a trekking trip in Poon Hill (Nepal), but had to cancel it amid the current situation. Couldn't reach the mountain so I decided to paint one instead. 🇳🇵 ⁠⠀
.⁠
Were any of your plans changed? 💭⁠
.⁠

Really like this one! ❤️. Yes many of my plans had to change due to this current situation. But, on the bright side your daily post makes me day so much happier! 🤗. Keep up the work 💪💪

Love your paintings, bright yet serene 🙌 I was planning to do Annapurna circuit later this year but will wait and see how things pan out! 🤷🏻‍♀️
Love love love the message. It's the exact same reason why I love hiking as well. 💜💜💜
@shaliciouz thank you so much! Appreciate it ☺️
@yumi.lovesfood glad you like it. Thank you 😊
